  "body": "instead of waiting for people to perform the steps to authorise Tudo (to access their GitHub orgs/issues we *could* request their GitHub username on the login page and initiate the retrieval of their issues *while* they are authenticating... That way, by the time they get back to Tudo their issues dashboard is already pre-rendered and loaded! This is a ***wow-factor*** people won't be *expecting* and thus our app immediately delivers on our first promise!\r\n\r\nThoughts?",
